        "heading": "Quality schooling that is affordable and inclusive",
        "body": "<p>A quality Catholic education is affordable and accessible for every family! As a guide, the cost of a Catholic education is around $6-$8 a day for primary and $11-$18 a day a day for a child in Year 7*. Significant discounts apply for sibli</p><p><strong>No child will be refused enrolment from a Catholic school because of a family's inability to pay school fees.</strong></p><p><a href=\"/our-schools/affordable-education\">Calculate my school fees</a></p>",
        "layout": "image-left",
        "image": {
          "src": "https://www.parra.catholic.edu.au/-/media/project/cedp/cathedparra/images/page-images/2021-rectangles/why-us-affordable.jpg",
